The President of the United States congratulates the people of Georgia on the inauguration of their new President, Giorgi Margvelashvili. He recognizes the contributions of outgoing President Mikheil Saakashvili and Prime Minister Bidzina Ivanishvili in strengthening Georgia's democratic institutions. The President also acknowledges Georgia's progress in consolidating democratic institutions and fulfilling its Euro-Atlantic aspirations. He calls on all of Georgia's political leaders to work together with civil society to build on this achievement.